title: The person who leaked Hillary Clinton's medical records was found dead
subtitle: A bogus news article played on a trick involving Hillary Clinton's "senior" medical records to write a story about the CIA finding the "dead man's key" on the computer of the deceased doctor's father.
author: Kim LaCapria
vclaim: The CIA found a "dead man's key" on the deceased father's computer for a doctor who treats Hillary Clinton from dementia.
